      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Google Calendar Intake\n\n1. Open **Poll Google Calendar**\n2. Create a **Header Auth** credential\n3. Header name: `X-Upshot-System-Secret`\n4. Value: the same private value stored in Supabase as `UPSHOT_SYSTEM_TRIGGER_SECRET`\n5. Save the credential\n6. Run **Test Calendar Intake** first\n7. The workflow starts in `dry_run: true` so it cannot create jobs\n8. After the dry run succeeds, change `dry_run` to `false` and activate the workflow\n\nThe 30 minute lookback overlaps every five minute poll. Existing execution idempotency prevents the same Google event from creating duplicate jobs.",
